           ++oo   local-user-file-view
           ++oo   local-user-shell
           ++oo   privacy-leak
           ++oo   remote-code-execution
           ++oo   remote-command-inject
           ++oo   remote-file-creation
           ++oo   remote-file-read
           ++oo   remote-file-view
           ++oo   remote-file-write
           ++oo   remote-key-theft
